Text: Please seed this! I'll seed it forever! Hot Rats contains Peaches En Regalia which is (in my opinion) the greatest Frank Zappa song!

This is FLAC format. PLEASE SEED it! I've gotta agree with Burnafro. Peaches en Regalia is one of Franks finest with NO pretense to commercialism. Wille the Pimp is also a standout track from Franks LONG career.
